# {{ project_name }}

> AI application scaffolded with [create-ai-project](https://github.com/tofayel/ai-scaffold)

**Profile:** `{{ profile }}` | **LLM:** `{{ llm_provider }}` ({{ llm_model }}) | **Vector DB:** `{{ vector_db }}`

## Quick Start

```bash
# 1. Copy and fill in environment variables
cp .env.example .env

# 2. Install dependencies
uv sync

# 3. Start the API
uv run uvicorn src.main:app --reload
```

API docs available at http://localhost:8000/docs

## Project Structure

```
{{ project_name }}/
├── src/
│   ├── main.py          # FastAPI entry point
│   ├── config.py        # Settings (pydantic-settings + .env)
│   ├── models.py        # Request / response schemas
{% if profile in ["rag", "full"] %}
│   ├── components/      # Retrieval: hybrid search + reranking
│   ├── services/        # Core logic: RAG pipeline, cache, routing
│   ├── prompts/         # Versioned prompt templates
│   └── security/        # Input / content / output guards
{% endif %}
{% if profile in ["agent", "full"] %}
│   ├── agents/          # Self-correcting agentic layer
│   └── agents/tools/    # Pluggable tool definitions
{% endif %}
{% if profile == "full" %}
├── evaluation/          # Golden dataset + offline/online eval
├── observability/       # Tracing, feedback, cost tracking
├── scripts/             # Seed, migrate, healthcheck
├── frontend/            # UI (containerized separately)
{% endif %}
├── tests/               # pytest test suite
└── docs/                # Architecture, API reference, deployment
```

## Environment Variables

Copy `.env.example` → `.env` and configure:

```bash
{% if llm_provider == "openai" %}
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...
{% elif llm_provider == "anthropic" %}
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...
{% elif llm_provider == "groq" %}
GROQ_API_KEY=gsk_...
{% elif llm_provider == "azure-openai" %}
AZURE_OPENAI_API_KEY=...
AZURE_OPENAI_ENDPOINT=https://...openai.azure.com/
{% endif %}
{% if vector_db == "pinecone" %}
PINECONE_API_KEY=...
{% elif vector_db == "pgvector" %}
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://user:pass@localhost:5432/{{ package_name }}
{% endif %}
```

## Development

```bash
uv run pytest                    # run tests
uv run ruff check src/ tests/    # lint
uv run mypy src/                 # type check
```

